{"tid":985713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太空寶石初現地球！以色列挖到全新礦物「迦密石」","createTime":"2019-01-18T00:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T03:49:57.000Z","uid":64191,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"916dfb6716f0e5b8fcd03bb7b3500e7b3029cc3e","tid":985713,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"以色列一間礦業公司，日前在該國北部瀕臨地中海的迦密山發現一種新礦物，其化學結構只曾在外太空見過，獲國際礦物學協會（IMA）承認是一種全新礦石「迦密石」（carmeltazite）。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，以色列一間礦業公司「Shefa Yamim」在迦密山發現一種全新礦物「迦密石」，這種礦石鑲嵌在藍寶石裡，主要成分為鈦、鋁及鋯，以往只在從外太空的隕石中發現這種成分組合，這是首次在地球發現同類物質，因其成分和晶體結構、性質必須與現有礦物相異，獲國際礦物學協會（IMA）承認是一種全新礦石，目前為止發現最大的「迦密石」為33.3克拉。<br />\n<br />\n「迦密石」藏身於藍寶石之中，色澤通常呈黑色、深綠色，目前尚不清楚其蘊藏有多大，礦業公司已獲以色列政府批准，將以「迦密藍寶石」之名，未來在市場推銷，由於寶石價格通常與其稀有性相關，因此該寶石可能會比鑽石更貴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2672405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2672405&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1np4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3a779b16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2672405&h=c881e1ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2672405</a>"},{"pid":"481d2ff2393442a0cb56e2566a675ff19f2aefe3","tid":985713,"uid":64191,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T00:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.haarets.co.il/image/upload/w_799,h_465,x_0,y_149,c_crop,g_north_west/w_609,h_343,q_auto,c_fill,f_auto/fl_any_format.preserve_transparency.progressive:none/v1546955914/1.6823958.3537042042.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.haarets.co.il%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fw_799%2Ch_465%2Cx_0%2Cy_149%2Cc_crop%2Cg_north_west%2Fw_609%2Ch_343%2Cq_auto%2Cc_fill%2Cf_auto%2Ffl_any_format.preserve_transparency.progressive%3Anone%2Fv1546955914%2F1.6823958.3537042042.jpg&h=36c736a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.timesofisrael.com/ww